{"tid":1566813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"913 死線已過，政府仍未有回應五大訴求，係時候升級","createTime":"2019-09-13T18:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T19:22:55.000Z","uid":1654,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3c053fb9b31970d6a2f634e4dec9fcc953774d","tid":1566813,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"915 維園見"},{"pid":"40579d4b026c64e9d82561b65db935033bd48fd2","tid":1566813,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:29:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0a011a8c5cd0cfd2c1413928f01d4d21d0d6eb6e","tid":1566813,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:30:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ad63330dce24c71a52abe31ef58938b570ef69b","tid":1566813,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d96f01de2ab3b5cbd42fefa24a661046012c66b2","tid":1566813,"uid":311193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:31:05.000Z","msg":"大家俾夠藉口自己未？"},{"pid":"c53f41a7580a8bf058519bbcddc57ea07429a919","tid":1566813,"uid":311193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:31:19.000Z","msg":"幾時全民full gear?"},{"pid":"668a3a091518c9b5a0af7832d63cbe6e5932977c","tid":1566813,"uid":311193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"唔係叫你帶gear上前線"},{"pid":"c50b63746964d8503610561aa4123fda2a4ce5e5","tid":1566813,"uid":311193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:32:09.000Z","msg":"係唔好再成為前線嘅負擔"},{"pid":"70d5d7fe6f4d83b9c80ef932e423178280ef81a1","tid":1566813,"uid":279616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e3c053fb9b31970d6a2f634e4dec9fcc953774d","tid":1566813,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"915 維園見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:39:20.000Z","msg":"The FIVE demands of the protest<br />\n<br />\n1. Full withdrawal of the extradition bill <br />\n<br />\n2. A commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality <br />\n<br />\n3. Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n4. Amnesty for arrested protesters <br />\n<br />\n5. Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and<br />\nthe Chief Executive <br />\n<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS,<br />\nNOT ONE LESS.<br />\nLIBERATE HONG KONG,<br />\nREVOLUTION OF OUR TIMES<br />\n<br />\n撇除政府問題，淨係計警隊，再淨係計721 85 811 新屋嶺  CCTV直送 831，已經夠哂理由比示威者做任何野，包括以武制暴 以眼還眼 百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，立即實行雙普選，推翻港共政權<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，但大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動<br />\n#抵制一切鐵路沿線所有商戶"},{"pid":"a4a08dd7a40efff1c60e99263ea9985a1a947af9","tid":1566813,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5NoYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5NoYN.jpg&h=6894a64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvUKrb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvUKrb8.jpg&h=ec6b4d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12點英領和平請願<br />\n灰磚範圍 英國領土</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2點打後 銅鑼灣自由活動!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【國際戰線】又係我，前英領職員，915見（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565523</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d93e014e31189648ed32784a2e38ef9da8e6f4c","tid":1566813,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:10:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8102c984f15ac8607932bdd4ef91ec3783d9b258","tid":1566813,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:22:55.000Z","msg":"大大力推"}]}